{"tid":772191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因為有同事無故被抄, 數百墨西哥工人集體離開地盤","createTime":"2018-08-08T14:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T19:00:32.000Z","uid":53705,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"47ab1e9650f2b87f5df6fbf9f330636c181e35b7","tid":772191,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"事件發生在上月31日，美國印第安納波利斯一間工廠其中一名管工被指是種族主義者，總是喜歡找非白人員工麻煩，常拍片或影相「捉痛腳」，務求趕走不聽話員工；當日他準備召開會議，要求一名墨西哥工人作翻譯，但遭到拒絕，他隨即取消會議並解僱5至6名工人。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳開後，工地內大批墨西哥裔工人不滿，紛紛執拾東西浩浩蕩蕩離開，為數大概多達百人，安東尼拿出了手機拍下這一幕，激讚「何其壯觀」！不一會，偌大的工地變得冷冷清清，安東尼說：「沒有人在磨碎、切割、焊接東西，墨西哥人關閉了這個該死的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拍片者不介意被炒<br />\n<br />\n更難能可貴的是，參與「出走」的工人並不屬於工會，顯得今次集體行動更加難能可貴。安東尼形容：「我感覺到力量，感覺很好。他們抬起頭來走了，真強！」<br />\n<br />\n據稱，有關影片在社交網上熱傳後，安東尼遭老闆威逼利誘，只要他把影片下架就可獲250美元，但他拒絕，結果自己也遭到解僱。安東尼並不在乎失去了工作，他認為工人應該獲得尊重，「我不喜歡種族主義者，不喜歡人們挑剔或欺凌其他人，這太荒謬了。」<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人應該試下學<br />\n如果有老細無故屌同事, 所有打工仔集體離開公司, 睇下老細有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81c289e8cd339ffcbb40ff8d8d350861265de43","tid":772191,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"樓主由你做起"},{"pid":"98ffc2db00f3451602ece720f35987e930e9f08a","tid":772191,"uid":18568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"聽日準時返工"},{"pid":"dcd2a4186572102f6cd01b8dbf690e8887ea0238","tid":772191,"uid":35014,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bfc890de7f994dc99266739de89732155b11991","tid":772191,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd2a4186572102f6cd01b8dbf690e8887ea0238","tid":772191,"uid":35014,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f344e4daab992c53824d209057b66555698bb9f3","tid":772191,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"如果香港人有e種凝聚力<br />\n<br />\nD賤種老闆仲會咁串"},{"pid":"6091e2f4a8d6e2bed6e142d7e36e005956a4107e","tid":772191,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"香港工人係勸你唔好幫口, 繼續做自己野"},{"pid":"f9a12ea421d3047a9057bf00e8421dcce472125a","tid":772191,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"香港真係好少見呢啲情況 一個部門一次過走三四個已經好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497488ba32b4dd227bfd3edc7d867ed0149e2485","tid":772191,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd2a4186572102f6cd01b8dbf690e8887ea0238","tid":772191,"uid":35014,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"呢樣真"},{"pid":"4138cba656752c48fc1cfab3f944c5bdd7f1b01b","tid":772191,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/224741_81561d6302278328e5defc29642fb07b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F224741_81561d6302278328e5defc29642fb07b.png&h=f52ee72b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05799f14f6ee0afb2d0943f36c33e446385aa5c6","tid":772191,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n一早話咩雨傘佔乜佔物痾尿無力咁<br />\n人唔駛多<br />\n九巴地鐵罷工都夠癱瘓你啦<br />\n三日你都跪低啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97135a4f2e3a2621fa75731000bc0c6046939af7","tid":772191,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81c289e8cd339ffcbb40ff8d8d350861265de43","tid":772191,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"s